# AUDIO::AUDIO_IS_SCRIPTED_MUSIC_PLAYING

## Summary
Returns true only if scripted music is currently playing

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This is an alias of AUDIO_IS_MUSIC_PLAYING.
